data.description: : This stunning Single Family home located in the desiredBramblewood Sub-Division . This household is part of the highly rated Lake Central schooldistrict. It boasts four bedrooms that includes a main level Master Bath with Whirlpool Tubplus an additional full bath and a half. Huge living room and a beautiful Modern Kitchenwith a generous 2,769 sq.ft provides plenty of space for relaxing and entertaining. Enjoyparking in an oversized 3 car heated garage. Full basement includes a roughed in additionalbath. This 2-story beauty sits on a spacious lot of 14,985 sq.ft., offering ample outdoorroom for activities and relaxation. Storage includes a walk in attic and shed. Don't miss outon the opportunity to own this well-maintained, move-in ready household.
